request.description:
## PATCH /rates/

This endpoint allows you to update the rates for both in-house and freelance drivers. The request body should include the updated rates structured according to the type of service (daily, bi-weekly, monthly) and the type of driver (in-house, freelance).

### Request Body

The request body must be in JSON format and should follow the structure below:

``` json
{
  "in_house_drivers": {
    "daily": {
      "one_way": <number>,
      "return": <number>
    },
    "bi_weekly": {
      "one_way": <number>,
      "return": <number>
    },
    "monthly": {
      "one_way": <number>,
      "return": <number>
    }
  },
  "freelance_drivers": {
    "daily": {
      "one_way": <number>,
      "return": <number>
    },
    "bi_weekly": {
      "one_way": <number>,
      "return": <number>
    },
    "monthly": {
      "one_way": <number>,
      "return": <number>
    }
  }
}

 ```

### Example Request Body

Here is an example of a request body to update the rates:

``` json
{
  "in_house_drivers": {
    "daily": {
      "one_way": 25,
      "return": 40
    },
    "bi_weekly": {
      "one_way": 220,
      "return": 400
    },
    "monthly": {
      "one_way": 400,
      "return": 700
    }
  },
  "freelance_drivers": {
    "daily": {
      "one_way": 20,
      "return": 35
    },
    "bi_weekly": {
      "one_way": 200,
      "return": 350
    },
    "monthly": {
      "one_way": 390,
      "return": 650
    }
  }
}

 ```

### Response

On a successful update, the server will respond with a status code of `200` and a JSON object indicating the updated rates. The response structure will look as follows:

``` json
{
  "in_house_drivers": {
    "daily": {
      "one_way": 0,
      "return": 0
    },
    "bi_weekly": {
      "one_way": 0,
      "return": 0
    },
    "monthly": {
      "one_way": 0,
      "return": 0
    }
  },
  "freelance_drivers": {
    "daily": {
      "one_way": 0,
      "return": 0
    },
    "bi_weekly": {
      "one_way": 0,
      "return": 0
    },
    "monthly": {
      "one_way": 0,
      "return": 0
    }
  },
  "_id": "",
  "createdAt": "",
  "__v": 0
}

 ```

This response confirms that the rates have been updated successfully.

